  <main class="main">

    <!-- Search results banner -->
    <div id="search-banner" style="display:none;background:var(--indigo-light);border:1px solid #C7D7FF;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 16px;margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px">
      <span id="search-label" style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--indigo)"></span>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" onclick="clearSearch()">✕ Clear</button>
    </div>

    <div class="tabs" id="main-tabs">
      <div class="tab active" onclick="showTab('tab-all',this)">All Questions</div>
      <div class="tab" onclick="showTab('tab-unans',this)">Unanswered</div>
      <div class="tab" onclick="showTab('tab-trend',this)">Trending 🔥</div>
      <div class="tab" onclick="showTab('tab-fac',this)">My Faculty</div>
    </div>

    <div data-tabs-container>

      <!-- ALL -->
      <div id="tab-all" data-tab>
        <div id="cards-container">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <a href="single-post.html" class="q-card card-hover" data-title="How does AVL tree rotation actually work?" data-faculty="IT" data-course="CS302">
            <div class="q-card-meta">
              <a href="user-profile.html?user=ahmad" onclick="event.stopPropagation()" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px">
                <div class="av av-sm"><img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/36?img=11" alt="Ahmad"></div>
                <span style="font-weight:600;font-size:13px">Ahmad K.</span>
              </a>
              <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-2)">· 2 hours ago</span>
              <span class="chip chip-indigo" style="margin-left:auto">IT Faculty</span>
              <span class="chip chip-violet">CS302</span>
              <span class="chip chip-emerald">✓ Solved</span>
            </div>
            <div class="q-card-title">How does AVL tree rotation actually work?</div>
            <div class="q-card-body clamp-2">I understand BST insertion but confused about AVL rotations (LL, LR, RR, RL) when height difference exceeds 1...</div>
            <div class="q-card-footer">
              <span>👍 42</span><span>💬 7 answers</span><span>👁️ 124 views</span>
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" style="margin-left:auto" onclick="event.stopPropagation();event.preventDefault();openSessionModal('Ahmad K.','https://i.pravatar.cc/60?img=11','CS302 — AVL Trees')">💬 Request Session</button>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <a href="single-post.html" class="q-card card-hover" data-title="Difference between Dijkstra and Bellman-Ford?" data-faculty="IT" data-course="CS401">
            <div class="q-card-meta">
              <a href="user-profile.html?user=rania" onclick="event.stopPropagation()" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px">
                <div class="av av-sm"><img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/36?img=20" alt="Rania"></div>
                <span style="font-weight:600;font-size:13px">Rania K.</span>
              </a>
              <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-2)">· 4 hours ago</span>
              <span class="chip chip-indigo" style="margin-left:auto">IT Faculty</span>
              <span class="chip chip-violet">CS401</span>
            </div>
            <div class="q-card-title">Difference between Dijkstra and Bellman-Ford?</div>
            <div class="q-card-body clamp-2">When should I use Dijkstra vs Bellman-Ford? I know Dijkstra is faster but when does Bellman-Ford become necessary?</div>
            <div class="q-card-footer">
              <span>👍 18</span><span>💬 4 answers</span><span>👁️ 87 views</span>
              <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" style="margin-left:auto" onclick="event.stopPropagation();event.preventDefault();openSessionModal('Rania K.','https://i.pravatar.cc/60?img=20','CS401 — Graph Algorithms')">💬 Request Session</button>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <a href="single-post.html" class="q-card card-hover" data-title="How to prepare a trial balance from journal entries?" data-faculty="Business" data-course="ACCT201">
            <div class="q-card-meta">
              <a href="user-profile.html?user=khalid" onclick="event.stopPropagation()" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px">
                <div class="av av-sm"><img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/36?img=33" alt="Khalid"></div>
                <span style="font-weight:600;font-size:13px">Khalid M.</span>
              </a>
              <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-2)">· 6 hours ago</span>
