              <a href="user-profile.html?user=lina" onclick="event.stopPropagation()" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px">
                <div class="av av-sm"><img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/36?img=47" alt="Lina"></div>
                <span style="font-weight:600;font-size:13px">Lina H.</span>
              </a>
              <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-2)">· 1 day ago</span>
              <span class="chip chip-violet" style="margin-left:auto">Engineering</span>
              <span class="chip chip-gray">MATH201</span>
            </div>
            <div class="q-card-title">Finding eigenvalues of a 3×3 matrix step by step?</div>
            <div class="q-card-body clamp-2">I need to find eigenvalues of a 3×3 matrix but the characteristic polynomial is getting complicated...</div>
